snippet.title: Meet CarryMinati | Episode 89
snippet.description:
YouTube Channel: https://m.youtube.com/@CarryMinati 

Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com

#carryminati

Lyrics:
Chamkeela angeelesi O Vadhiney
Chaaku lekkundetodey O Vadhiney
Kandlaku ainaa betti kaththoley
Kannetla koduthundeney
Sinigina baneeneysi O Vadhiney
Nattintla koosuntadey O Vadhiney
Maasina lungi yesi ippudu
Manchamlaney pantadey

Pendlaina koththala aththarlu poosinney
Nee seera singhulu patti yenakenaka thiriginney
Muddhulisthundey poolu thesthundey
Sakkera lekka nee maatalumtundey
Maarey nee theeru perigey nee noru
Mandhukalavaataithiney

Kadupula intha bosi O Vadhiney
Koduthadey bandakesi O Vadhiney
Amavaasa punnaaniko atlatla
Akkaraku pakkakoththadammo

Kanta neeranna pettakunda santibidda lekka
Ninnu Aluguthuntey boodharakiyyaledhaa
Nuvvu seetiki maatiki gintha dhaanni ganthajeysi
Ijjathamtha bazaarlesthalevaa

Yem gaali sokeno‚Ä¶veenneththi thirigeno..
Paathabaddanemo chethanaitha ledho
Ultaa nannitla mandhi mungatla badhnaam jeththadu

Noridisi adagadhuraa baammardhi
Cheppindhi cheyyadhuraa baammardhi
Pakkintla koosuntadhi naa meedha
Chaadeelu chepthuntadhi
Naa gonthu kosindrantu bammardhi
Sokaalu peduthuntadhi bammardhi
Muchchatlu jeppabothey meeyakka
Moothantha thipputhuntadhi

Seekatla unnaa vaakitla unnaa
Kantiki reppoley kaasthadu mogadu
Yentha lollaina nuvventa untey
Yedhuru nilsi vaadu gelsi vasthaadu
Gosalni joostha unnaa yedhainaa
Gundella dhaasthaaduley
Nee bottu nee gaajuley yenthainaa
Vaani paanaaluley

snippet.title: Quetta Gladiators vs Multan Sultans | Highlights | Pakistan Super League | 11th March 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv
 
Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3V8TM1y

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-pakistan-super-league-1700001151

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

A total of 515 runs were scored in the 40 overs and it was the highest match aggregate in T20 cricket in the world. Usman Khan scored the fastest century in PSL which helped the Multan Sultans to reach a massive total of 262 runs. Quetta Gladiators showcased the same energy while chasing and were able to reach close to the target but Abbas Afridi's five-wicket haul made the difference in the end.

Tere Bin Episode 21 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 8th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Director: Siraj ul Haq

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

snippet.description:
Episode 3716: Khujli Powder Ka Sach
--------------------------------------------------------
Dr. Hathi comes to Bhide's rescue as he has been continuously itching. Dr. Hathi asks Tapu Sena to put water on Bhide and asks Abdul to get some fresh soil from the garden. Everyone is shocked to see the new style of treating a patient with itchiness. Later Dr. Hathi asks Bhide to apply the soil on his body and asks him to go for a bath. Bhide comes back and to everyone's surprise, he has got rid of the itching. Dr. Hathi announces that this was not due to the gulal powder, Bhide realizes that he had applied some oil on his body before coming for the Holi festival. Madhavi is shocked as the oil had expired and she had thrown the oil bottle. Stay tuned.

Tere Bin Episode 22 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 9th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Tere Bin Episode 23 Teaser - 9th March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Sharjah Shake is a popular milkshake that originated in the city of Kozhikode in the Kerala state. It is a creamy and flavourful beverage that is made with a combination of milk, banana, sugar, and boost. Some of the most common flavourings used in Sharjah Shake include peanuts, cashew nuts, and dates, which give the shake a rich and aromatic taste.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3715 - 10 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3715: Tension Ke Rang
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide accuses Tapu of mixing itching powder in the 'gulaal' to trouble him. The members of the Gokuldham society wait for Dr. Hathi in order to treat Bhide and get rid of the itchiness. Inspector Chaalu Pandey makes a surprise visit to the society and questions Bhide about his unusual behavior, everyone is shocked as they assume that Bhide has filed an official complaint at the police station. Inspector Chaalu Pandey orders to file an FIR against Tapu for troubling people at the festival. Champaklal and Jethalal get angry and ask Bhide to withdraw his complaint. Bhide who is struggling with the itchiness on his body is unable to say and react to the issue as he wants to clarify that he has not called the police. Stay tuned.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3715, 10 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. snippet.title: Best International Women's Day | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
International Women's Day (IWD) is a global day celebrating the social, economic, cultural and political achievements of women. The day also marks a call to action for accelerating gender parity.
Marked annually on March 8th, IWD is one of the most important days of the year to, celebrate women's achievements, educate and awareness raise for women's equality, call for positive change advancing women.

snippet.title: 'Visiting India Was Like Stepping Into The Future': Pakistani Foreign Policy Expert
snippet.description:
#pakistan #foreignpolicy #uzairyunus #podcaster #digitalpayments #qrcode 
Pakistani foreign policy expert Uzair Younus lauded India‚Äôs digital development saying that his first-hand experience of the expanding digital footprint in India during a recent visit to the country made him feel like he was visiting a state from the future. The Pakistani foreign policy expert expressed how impressed he was when he saw a cobbler in Mumbai offering a QR code scanner to his customers to enable digital payment. He said, "A paan shop owner also had a QR code scanner. Cash was not needed at all." Younus asserted that he watched in awe as people had kachoris at eateries and seem to leave just like that. He said he was first wondering why the customers are leaving without paying for their meals, it him later that they had done so digitally.
‚ÄúI was wondering why the shopkeeper was allowing his customers to leave without paying for their meals. Then I saw that there was a PayTm QR code and the customers were simply scanning the code to make the payments,‚Äù he added.

Watch the full interview here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KOIrdgLHLZE

The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. snippet.title: Peshawar Zalmi vs Quetta Gladiators | Highlights | Pakistan Super League | 8th March 2023
snippet.description:
Peshawar Zalmi batted superbly and posted a mammoth total of 240 runs at the end of their innings. Captain Babar Azam was the star with a century to his name. Peshawar Zalmi looked like the winners even before Quetta Gladiators came to bat, however, Jason Roy had other plans. The opener looked unstoppable as he was dealing in boundaries and went on to make 145 runs from just 63 deliveries. This power-packed knock helped the Quetta Gladiators to win by 8 wickets and 10 balls remaining. 
.
.

snippet.title: Kuch Itne Haseen - Priyanka Chahar Choudhary | Ankit Gupta | Yasser Desai |Rajat N | Samay | Harsh
snippet.description:
Anshul Garg presents Kuch Itne Haseen featuring Priyanka Chahar Choudhary and Ankit Gupta

This captivating love story will surely leave you with a mushy feeling inside.

Stream here : https://INgrooves.lnk.to/KuchItneHaseen

Song : Kuch Itne Haseen
Singer : Yasser Desai
Lyrics : Samay
Composer : Harsh Kargeti
Music : Rajat Nagpal
Guitars : Shomu Seal 
Flute : Kiran 
Mixed by Rajat Nagpal 
Mastered by Naweed @ Whitfield Mastering , London 
Recorded by Rahul Sharma assist by Samir Dharap at Studio 504

Featuring Priyanka Chahar Choudhary and Ankit Gupta

Producer : Anshul Garg

Directed By : Agam Mann & Azeem Mann 
Project Head : Raghav Sharma
Project Manager : Gaurav Bharti, Gaurav Arora, Ashima Chauhaan
DOP : Shinda Singh 
Production : RS Films and Production 
Choreographer : John 
Art Director : Pinky Arts
AD's : Rajat Yadav, Sandy
Production Assistants : Jadu, Rohit, Honey 
Stills : Akki Blueskyfilmz
Child artist casting : ELVIN ART ACADEMY "RAJPURA"
Child artists : Ghazal, Saanvi, Eyaan, Samar
Priest : Rajat Sindhi

Lyrics

Dekh kar humein duniya ye kitni hairaan hai 
Mazak nahi ye bandhan ye Khuda ka ehsaan hai 
Ho Bhari Mohabbat Dekho. Dekho har baat mein 

Kuch itne haseen hain hum, haseen hum sath mein 
 
Dhoop lage jo tumko sar Par chaon ban jayege 
Kaanto Par chalna bejijhak tere paon ban jayege  
Haar kar na haare waisi haar jaisa hota hai 
Ye jaana tumse mil kar jaana pyar Kaisa hota hai  
Ho Chand chamakta jaise, jaise Ho raat mein 
  
Kuch itne haseen hain hum, haseen hum sath mein 
 
Sada hi sath rahege, samay ka paimaan hai 
Ishq bhara mausam mein mausam bhi bayimaan hai 
Mitti aur khusbhu jaise, jaise barsaat mein,  
Kuch itne Haseen hain hum, Haseen hum sath mein

Follow PlayDMF on Instagram : https://bit.ly/PlayDMFonIG

#priyankachaharchoudhary #ankitgupta #yasserdesai

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises
